          <p>SoundMelon is a social media platform that empowers a community of artists and music lovers to connect and share the music they love and create.</p>
          <p>
            Our goals are far and wide, so to kick off this long journey we’ve launched
            <span>SoundMelon Radio,</span>
            the first piece of the puzzle. It’s so terribly simple to use, anyone with a melon could do it!
          </p>
          <p></p>
          <div class='indented'>
            <p>
              <span class='number'>1</span>
              Go to
              <a href='http://www.soundmelon.com'>www.soundmelon.com</a>
              and connect with your Facebook account. In connecting, we learn a little bit about what sort of music you like and what city you live in; it's how we connect you to music around you.
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class='number'>2</span>
              You’re now online with the radio! Hitting play will start playing out tunes that are tailored to your tastes from artists around you. You might hear a song by a band one morning and be able to watch a show of theirs that night!
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class='number'>3</span>
              If you’re an artist, just use the handy dandy add music link at the bottom to connect your SoundMelon account to SoundCloud or YouTube and within seconds your tunes are on the radio!
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            We have so many ideas in the hopper, this is only the beginning. Come on this ride with us, listen to some tunes, provide some feedback and let us know how you feel. Get meloning at
            <a href='http://www.soundmelon.com'>www.soundmelon.com.</a>
          </p>
